>https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210301/3YOSNT3N7BCMRO6I7QBNUV7JV4/</a><br />\n<br />\n趙婷出生於中國北京，自認少女時期很反叛，喜歡看漫畫、寫小說、看電影，反覆看了無數次王家衛的《春光乍洩》，推崇該片對她有關鍵性影響。15歲時，不諳英語的她被父母送到倫敦就讀寄宿學校，但她嚮往的卻是到美國過自由生活，後來又搬到洛杉磯讀完高中，之後她修讀政治科學系，於紐約大學蒂施藝術學院碩士班攻讀電影製片。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n97年佢15歲，香港人仲on99民主回歸，大導演已經知邊度有自由，抵佢彈起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c549883df53c84c98f3482e1547ed5ca3527ce","tid":2427762,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:00:16.000Z","msg":"北京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地不知幾想搣甩支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d35d5d49606c18cebe5a5a98233c3b85e79dd7","tid":2427762,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:00:32.000Z","msg":"一律當外國人處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n富爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9fe092a98a83ff861471af3380b0ce35833d7e6","tid":2427762,"uid":28432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b89966e7a81687d9973c74fae91962e5eade9de0","tid":2427762,"uid":41343,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T05:00:50.000Z","msg":"女導演14歲喺北京讀書唔成<br />\n國際學校都唔考慮，同屋企人講要去英國，就飛去讀三十萬學費一年嘅寄宿學校，做冤大頭幫英國輸血<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://xw.qq.com/cmsid/20201219A0HVAW00?f=newdc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fxw.qq.com%2Fcmsid%2F20201219A0HVAW00%3Ff%3Dnewdc&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3RYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=ce9487ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://xw.qq.com/cmsid/20201219A0HVAW00?f=newdc</a><br />\n<br />\n然後去英國做二等公民都唔夠，再飛去美國做二等公民，聲稱唔靠父母一路讀上去，自己籌錢拍電影，終於名成利就，勵志呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:06:51.000Z","msg":"睇完套戲 好似拎住個頒獎禮拎獎戲check list逐項剔住嚟拍 <br />\n好撚老土呢啲戲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb044f65ce3fd3d8cef8f69b6002f4249ae33bf3","tid":2427762,"uid":121076,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:07:48.000Z","msg":"崇洋媚外<br />\n點解唔係去中央藝術學院？點解要去美國攞獎？<br />\n小粉紅呢? 失哂蹤? 見人地後台硬就啞哂?"},{"pid":"cd55d8cc5d5562f9af4f465ec1024beb74be13b1","tid":2427762,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2d35d5d49606c18cebe5a5a98233c3b85e79dd7","tid":2427762,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:00:32.000Z","msg":"一律當外國人處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n富爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:10:10.000Z","msg":"黨二代唔知乜鳩方法過去英國=炎黃子孫吐氣揚眉<br />\n<br />\nBNO Visa = 黃屍狗！走去俾英國佬呃錢！人財兩空！"}]}